snippet.title: NZ Vs PAK 1st T20i | Cricket Highlights | Pakistan Tour Of New Zealand | 16th March 2025
snippet.description:
In the 1st T20I, New Zealand won the toss and decided to bowl first and invited Pakistan to bat first. Pakistan was cheaply dismissed on the score of 91 runs in 18.4 overs. New Zealand chased down the target in just 10.1 overs and won the match by 9 wickets. 
.

snippet.title: Sunita Williams Smiles And Waves At The Camera After Her Safe Return To Earth
snippet.description:
NASA astronauts Sunita Williams and Butch Wilmore have successfully returned to Earth after 9 months in in space. The SpaceX capsule 'Freedom' splashed down at 3:28 a.m., concluding a mission extended due to technical issues. The landing, involving complex de-orbiting and seven crucial phases, proceeded as planned. The astronauts will undergo medical examinations upon return.

snippet.description:

Aas Paas Episode 17 - [Eng Sub] - Laiba Khan - Ali Ansari - 18th March 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Aas Paas is a story of love, sacrifice, and the struggles within the relationships we often take for granted.
Arshia, a strong-willed young woman, is determined to reunite her broken family after her father abandons them. Meanwhile, Dr. Saham, a dedicated professional carrying his own burdens,
crosses paths with her.
Bound by their selflessness, they embark on a journey where their devotion to family is tested, and their own happiness is put on the line.
Will Arshia succeed in bringing her family back together? What challenges await Dr. Saham and Arshia? Could love blossom between them?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Muhammad Iftikhar Iffi
Writer: Samra Bukhari

Cast:

snippet.description:
Special Guest - Paresh Ganatra
Paresh Ganatra is an Indian actor and comedian known for his work in television, films, and theater. He began his acting career during his college days by performing in theater. Paresh made his film debut in 1999 with "Mann" and gained prominence for his role as Praveen Thakkar in the TV series "Baa Bahoo Aur Baby" (2005‚Äì2010). He is also known for his performances in films like "No Entry" (2005), "Welcome" (2007), and "Rowdy Rathore" (2012).

Apart from movies and daily soaps, Paresh Ganatra is also well-known for his particiaption in the comedy reality TV shows like ‚ÄúComedy Circus 3 Ka Tadka,‚Äù ‚ÄúComedy Circus Mahasangram,‚Äù and ‚ÄúComedy Circus Ke SuperStars.‚Äù He has also played different characters in ‚ÄúComedy Nights with Kapil‚Äù (2013‚Äì2016), and ‚ÄúThe Kapil Sharma Show‚Äù (2016‚Äì2017).

snippet.title: NASA‚Äôs SpaceX Crew-9 Undocking
snippet.description:
Watch as the four members of NASA's SpaceX Crew-9 mission‚ÄîNASA astronauts Nick Hague, Suni Williams, Butch Wilmore, and cosmonaut Aleksandr Gorbunov‚Äîundock from the International Space Station and begin their journey home to Earth.

Crew-9's SpaceX Dragon spacecraft is scheduled to undock from the International Space Station at 1:05 a.m. EST (0505 UTC). After undocking from the station, Crew-9 is scheduled to splash down off the coast of Florida at 5:57 p.m. EDT (2157 UTC), ending their multi-month mission in low Earth orbit.

See the full schedule for Crew-9's return to Earth: https://go.nasa.gov/4iWeg8N
Learn more about Crew-9's scientific mission: https://go.nasa.gov/4bWdt5u
Follow the latest Crew-9 mission updates: https://www.nasa.gov/blogs/commercialcrew/

Credit: NASA

snippet.description:
Part two of #prithvirajsukumaran's interview with Baradwaj Rangan covers a wide range of topics, including how directing aids his acting, how the film industry has been a soft target for everyone, why he didn't pursue awards and prizes, working with his actors, why multi-starrers aren't happening in the Malayalam industry these days, how he deals with hate and success, whether reviews matter, and much more.

snippet.title: Tigmanshu Dhulia's The Promise ‚Äì A Must-Watch | Royal Stag Barrel Select Shorts
snippet.description:
In Tigmanshu Dhulia's poignant masterpiece ‚ÄòThe Promise,‚Äô Royal Stag Barrel Select Shorts delivers a soul-stirring tale that exemplifies the best of select storytelling.

When Delhi newcomer Chitra (played by Priyamani) crosses paths with George (played by Jim Sarbh), a bartender from Greater Kailash 1, an unexpected connection blossoms. As they share fragments of their pasts, their bond deepens, transcending fleeting moments into something profound and unspoken. But fate has other plans. George receives his long-awaited M.Tech acceptance letter, and in a moment of quiet heartbreak, Chitra chooses to step away, ensuring he pursues his dreams. Their farewell is sealed with a promise‚Äîto meet again at the same place, 20 years later.

Two decades pass. George returns to the same place, carrying the weight of the past and the anticipation of what lies ahead. But what he discovers changes everything. ‚ÄòThe Promise‚Äô is not just a story‚Äîit‚Äôs an emotional journey that lingers, reminding us that some bonds are meant to withstand the test of time.

‚ÄòThe Promise‚Äô stands as a testament to select filmmaking‚Äîwhere nuanced emotions, evolved storytelling techniques, and sophisticated narrative choices elevate cinema beyond mainstream conventions.

snippet.title: Sunita Williams Countdown to Earth üî• üöÄ | Madan Gowri | Tamil | MG Squad üññüèª
snippet.description:
In this video, Madan Gowri explains the highly anticipated return of astronaut Sunita Williams after spending months in space aboard the International Space Station (ISS). After her 9-month mission, she is set to return to Earth safely soon, facing a re-entry through Earth‚Äôs atmosphere. This process exposes astronauts to extreme G-forces, pushing their bodies to the limit. After months in microgravity, astronauts experience muscle loss, weakened bones, and balance issues, making the transition back to Earth‚Äôs gravity a major challenge. The final stage of her return? A high-speed descent and a dramatic splashdown in the ocean. Even after landing, she‚Äôll need time to recover from space travel. But how does NASA prepare astronauts for this? What changes will she face during re-entry and splashdown? Will it be a smooth landing or a bumpy ride back home? This return will test her mental and physical endurance like never before.  With space exploration expanding towards the Moon, Mars, and beyond, missions like these are crucial for the future of human spaceflight. Could India play a role in future interplanetary missions? Stay tuned to find out!

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Aas Paas Episode 15 - [Eng Sub] - Laiba Khan - Ali Ansari - 16th March 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Aas Paas is a story of love, sacrifice, and the struggles within the relationships we often take for granted.
Arshia, a strong-willed young woman, is determined to reunite her broken family after her father abandons them. Meanwhile, Dr. Saham, a dedicated professional carrying his own burdens,
crosses paths with her.
Bound by their selflessness, they embark on a journey where their devotion to family is tested, and their own happiness is put on the line.
Will Arshia succeed in bringing her family back together? What challenges await Dr. Saham and Arshia? Could love blossom between them?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Muhammad Iftikhar Iffi
Writer: Samra Bukhari

Cast:
Ali Ansari as Dr. Saham
Laiba Khan as Arshia/Arshi
Samina Ahmed as Aneeqa Begum
Saba Faisal as Seemab

Aas Paas Episode 15 - [Eng Sub] - Laiba Khan - Ali Ansari - 16th March 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Aas Paas is a story of love, sacrifice, and the struggles within the relationships we often take for granted.
Arshia, a strong-willed young woman, is determined to reunite her broken family after her father abandons them. Meanwhile, Dr. Saham, a dedicated professional carrying his own burdens,
crosses paths with her.
Bound by their selflessness, they embark on a journey where their devotion to family is tested, and their own happiness is put on the line.
Will Arshia succeed in bringing her family back together? What challenges await Dr. Saham and Arshia? Could love blossom between them?

Never underestimate the power of freakin' lasers! Have fun learning to think like an engineer and get 2 FREE boxes at: http://crunchlabs.com/Lidar

Get your CrunchLabs box today:
Build Box for kids click here: http://crunchlabs.com/Lidar

Full un-cut footage from the fake wall crash: https://x.com/MarkRober/status/1901449395327094898

The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.
